{"tid":853352,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"17歲那日不要臉 參加了股市","createTime":"2018-10-08T13:55:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T16:46:16.000Z","uid":103759,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"12ec2d2fffbe3c84feb8c11aa4e5992e72f76cd0","tid":853352,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:55:23.000Z","msg":"17歲那日不要臉 參加了股市<br />\n牛熊也有訓練班 短短一年太新鮮<br />\n記得麵仔 化雲 都已見過面<br />\n後來...榮升主角太突然<br />\n<br />\n廿九歲破產的晚宴 Fans太瘋癲<br />\n來聽我唱段情歌一曲 歌詞太經典<br />\n我的call輪 牛熊早已太熟練<br />\n然而財演總唱不厭<br />\n<br />\n唱這歌 齊齊來一遍<br />\n無時無刻都記住匯豐響遍天<br />\n來唱這歌 由從頭再一遍<br />\n如情濃有點 淚流難避免<br />\n音階起跌 拍子改變<br />\n每首歌 是每張臉<br />\n<br />\n唱這歌 齊齊來一遍<br />\n無時無刻都記住騰訊響遍天<br />\n來唱情歌 由從頭再一遍<br />\n如情濃有點 淚流難避免<br />\n音階起跌 拍子改變<br />\n年月變 但我未變<br />\n<br />\n如今我四十看從前 炒燶了股票<br />\n回憶我冀望那牛熊都依然到今天<br />\n那首匯豐 700 不再經典<br />\n仍長埋你的心中從未變<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793eaf59c83549a9db6d1dd990ff3c8646718039","tid":853352,"uid":13288,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:58:58.000Z","msg":"邊間教會"},{"pid":"9ade23b4e71837d2ec2c90bfc5adf2c7adfc45bf","tid":853352,"uid":55533,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T14:01:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.imgur.com/VPzWfjR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVPzWfjR.jpg&h=4d36305b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.imgur.com/DdJzqJQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https